                  "OwningCycle": null,
                  "Name": "Adult",
                  "Children": [
                    {
                      "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
                      "Text": "**Adult - not up to date**\n\nMostly above-ground around the plant (aggregate around clover plants) or on the soil surface, \n\nMobility - fly in and fly out (driven by wind/weather)\n\nEats clover (white and red) leaves\n\nDevelopment driven by thermal time and food availability (latter not yet implemented)\n\nMortality from:\n\n- too hot\n\n- too dry\n\n- too wet\n\n- too old\n\n- predation (beetles, spiders)\n\n- parasitism (wasp)\n\n- disease (general, population dependent and seasonal with higher values in autumn)\n\nMate frequently\n\nLay eggs (broadcast around the plants they feed on)\n\nOverwinter as adults\n\n\n",
                      "Name": "Memo",
                      "Children": [],
                      "IncludeInDocumentation": true,
                      "Enabled": true,
                      "ReadOnly": false
                    },
